    },
    {
      "item_id": "768a73bfee:9",
      "text": "：Attach to RenderMan PxrDomeLight（连接到 RenderMan PxrDomeLight）",
      "ascii_letters": 50,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "768a73bfee:10",
      "text": "Overview（资源概览）",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "768a73bfee:11",
      "text": "HDR Vault 是 Philip Modin 的作品。它们属于 public domain，并且已经由 Leo Frison 预先 converted。",
      "ascii_letters": 49,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "768a73bfee:13",
      "text": "这个 resource 设计为与 RenderMan 的",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "768a73bfee:14",
      "text": "Preset Browser",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "768a73bfee:17",
      "text": "Asset Library > EnvironmentMaps",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "768a73bfee:18",
      "text": "folder。文件按 category 组织，可以在 preset browser 中轻松搜索。",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "768a73bfee:20",
      "text": "RenderManAssetLibrary",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "768a73bfee:21",
      "text": "folder 转移到具有 full writing privileges 的位置。",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "768a73bfee:22",
      "text": "当你转移 Materials folder 并把 Asset Library 移到其他位置后，重要的是通过 Maya preferences 告诉 Maya 使用新的 path。",
      "ascii_letters": 50,
      "cjk_chars": 25
    },
    {
      "item_id": "768a73bfee:23",
      "text": "或者，你可以在 Maya.env file 中创建新的 environment variable，以确保始终指向正确的 folder：",
      "ascii_letters": 36,
      "cjk_chars": 21
    },
    {
      "item_id": "768a73bfee:25",
      "text": "Public Domain. Free of known copyright restrictions.（公有领域，无已知版权限制。）",
      "ascii_letters": 44,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    }
  ],
